Class 3D graphics card with 256 MB of memory or vyshe.Google SketchUP Pro - a professional version of the software, which lets you create 3D-models, show them as presentations, share them. The program will be useful wherever there is need to use of 3D-models, whether it be designing an extension to the house, student learning geometry or the creation of models for Google Earth. A set of simple tools and involving intellectual paint system makes it easy to create and edit models, export, create a video or print the results. Instead of imposing the values ??of the coordinates, you can use the multi-function control system location of the object by means of labels, text prompts, lines of different colors. Using the tools as close to real life, is not it much easier to learn and, most importantly, remember how to use them.


Features:
=========

- Draw, edit, measure, rotate, and scale figures.
- Divide the model into sections for internal parts.
- Apply the model pre textures or create your own.
- Fill the prepared model components (trees, cars, doors and windows, people), or create your own.
- retouch a face.
- Simulate a shadow in real time for any earthly object.
- Simulate the location of cameras.
- Implement a virtual view.
- Conduct a tour presentation.
- Import-dimensional images (. Jpg,. Png,. Tif,. Tga,. Bmp) and three-dimensional models (.3 ds,. Dem,. Ddf,. Dwg,. Dxf,. Skp).
- Export models in Google Earth.
- Export models of two-dimensional images (. Jpg,. Bmp,. Png,. Tif).
- Stop the print model.
- Develop additional applications in the environment of Ruby.
The main functions of SketchUp:
- Export models formats 3DS, DWG, DXF, OBJ, XSI, VRML and FBX.
- Export animation and virtual review format MOV and AVI.
- Support for organic modeling (Sandbox) and functions of Film & Stage.
- Import and export of GIS-data.
- Print and export raster images at higher resolution screen.
